32struct _gss_mechanism_cred {
33 HEIM_SLIST_ENTRY(_gss_mechanism_cred) gmc_link;
34 gssapi_mech_interface gmc_mech; /* mechanism ops for MC */
35 gss_OID gmc_mech_oid; /* mechanism oid for MC */
36 gss_cred_id_t gmc_cred; /* underlying MC */
37};
38HEIM_SLIST_HEAD(_gss_mechanism_cred_list, _gss_mechanism_cred);
39
40struct _gss_cred {
41 struct _gss_mechanism_cred_list gc_mc;
42};
43
44struct _gss_mechanism_cred *
45_gss_copy_cred(struct _gss_mechanism_cred *mc);
46
47struct _gss_mechanism_name;
48
49OM_uint32
50_gss_acquire_mech_cred(OM_uint32 *minor_status,
51 gssapi_mech_interface m,
52 const struct _gss_mechanism_name *mn,
53 gss_const_OID credential_type,
54 const void *credential_data,
55 OM_uint32 time_req,
56 gss_const_OID desired_mech,
57 gss_cred_usage_t cred_usage,
58 struct _gss_mechanism_cred **output_cred_handle);
